    <條號>Article 37</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Act shall come into force from the date of promulgation, while the implementation of the amendments made to Articles 3, 5, 13 to 15, 17, 18 and 32, which were promulgated on May 7, 1997; and the amendments made to Articles 12 which were promulgated on Oct.31, 2001, shall come into force when determined by the Executive Yuan.
